{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#Substring.Raw.Legacy.contains\"><span class=\"name\">Substring</span>.<span class=\"name\">Raw</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">contains</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Substring.Raw\">Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Checks whether a substring contains the specified character.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#Substring.Raw.Legacy.contains","kind":"def","line":510,"name":"Substring.Raw.Legacy.contains","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L510-L518"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#Substring.Raw.Legacy.all\"><span class=\"name\">Substring</span>.<span class=\"name\">Raw</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">all</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Substring.Raw\">Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Checks whether the Boolean predicate `p` returns `true` for every character in a substring.\n\nShort-circuits at the first character for which `p` returns `false`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#Substring.Raw.Legacy.all","kind":"def","line":498,"name":"Substring.Raw.Legacy.all","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L498-L508"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#Substring.Raw.Legacy.any\"><span class=\"name\">Substring</span>.<span class=\"name\">Raw</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">any</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Substring.Raw\">Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Checks whether the Boolean predicate `p` returns `true` for any character in a substring.\n\nShort-circuits at the first character for which `p` returns `true`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#Substring.Raw.Legacy.any","kind":"def","line":485,"name":"Substring.Raw.Legacy.any","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L485-L496"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#Substring.Raw.Legacy.foldr\"><span class=\"name\">Substring</span>.<span class=\"name\">Raw</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">foldr</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">init</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Substring.Raw\">Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Folds a function over a substring from the right, accumulating a value starting with `init`. The\naccumulated value is combined with each character in reverse order, using `f`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#Substring.Raw.Legacy.foldr","kind":"def","line":473,"name":"Substring.Raw.Legacy.foldr","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L473-L483"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#Substring.Raw.Legacy.foldl\"><span class=\"name\">Substring</span>.<span class=\"name\">Raw</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">foldl</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">init</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Substring.Raw\">Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Folds a function over a substring from the left, accumulating a value starting with `init`. The\naccumulated value is combined with each character in order, using `f`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`. Its runtime behavior is equivalent to that of `Substring.Raw.foldl`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#Substring.Raw.Legacy.foldl","kind":"def","line":461,"name":"Substring.Raw.Legacy.foldl","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L461-L471"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.contains\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">contains</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Checks whether a string contains the specified character.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n\nExamples:\n* `\"green\".contains 'e' = true`\n* `\"green\".contains 'x' = false`\n* `\"\".contains 'x' = false`\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.contains","kind":"def","line":442,"name":"String.Legacy.contains","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L442-L455"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.all\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">all</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Checks whether the Boolean predicate `p` returns `true` for every character in a string.\n\nShort-circuits at the first character for which `p` returns `false`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n\nExamples:\n * `\"brown\".all (·.isLetter) = true`\n * `\"brown and orange\".all (·.isLetter) = false`\n * `\"\".all (fun _ => false) = true`\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.all","kind":"def","line":425,"name":"String.Legacy.all","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L425-L440"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.any\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">any</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Checks whether there is a character in a string for which the Boolean predicate `p` returns `true`.\n\nShort-circuits at the first character for which `p` returns `true`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n\nExamples:\n * `\"brown\".any (·.isLetter) = true`\n * `\"brown\".any (·.isWhitespace) = false`\n * `\"brown and orange\".any (·.isLetter) = true`\n * `\"\".any (fun _ => false) = false`\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.any","kind":"def","line":407,"name":"String.Legacy.any","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L407-L423"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.anyAux\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">anyAux</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">stopPos</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Auxuliary definition for `String.Legacy.any`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.anyAux","kind":"def","line":390,"name":"String.Legacy.anyAux","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L390-L405"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.foldr\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">foldr</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">init</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Folds a function over a string from the right, accumulating a value starting with `init`. The\naccumulated value is combined with each character in reverse order, using `f`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n\nExamples:\n * `\"coffee tea water\".foldr (fun c n => if c.isWhitespace then n + 1 else n) 0 = 2`\n * `\"coffee tea and water\".foldr (fun c n => if c.isWhitespace then n + 1 else n) 0 = 3`\n * `\"coffee tea water\".foldr (fun c s => c.push s) \"\" = \"retaw dna aet eeffoc\"`\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.foldr","kind":"def","line":374,"name":"String.Legacy.foldr","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L374-L388"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.foldrAux\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">foldrAux</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i </span><span class=\"fn\">begPos</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Auxuliary definition for `String.Legacy.foldr`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.foldrAux","kind":"def","line":356,"name":"String.Legacy.foldrAux","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L356-L372"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.revFind\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">revFind</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Finds the position of the last character in a string for which the Boolean predicate `p` returns\n`true`. If there is no such character in the string, then `none` is returned.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n\nExamples:\n * `\"coffee tea water\".revFind (·.isWhitespace) = some ⟨10⟩`\n * `\"tea\".revFind (· == 'X') = none`\n * `\"\".revFind (· == 'X') = none`\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.revFind","kind":"def","line":340,"name":"String.Legacy.revFind","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L340-L354"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.revFindAux\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">revFindAux</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">pos</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Auxuliary definition for `String.Legacy.revFind`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.revFindAux","kind":"def","line":324,"name":"String.Legacy.revFindAux","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L324-L338"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.find\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">find</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Finds the position of the first character in a string for which the Boolean predicate `p` returns\n`true`. If there is no such character in the string, then the end position of the string is\nreturned.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n\nExamples:\n * `\"coffee tea water\".find (·.isWhitespace) = ⟨6⟩`\n * `\"tea\".find (· == 'X') = ⟨3⟩`\n * `\"\".find (· == 'X') = ⟨0⟩`\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.find","kind":"def","line":307,"name":"String.Legacy.find","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L307-L322"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.findAux\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">findAux</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">stopPos </span><span class=\"fn\">pos</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Auxuliary definition for `String.Legacy.find`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.findAux","kind":"def","line":291,"name":"String.Legacy.findAux","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L291-L305"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.revPosOf\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">revPosOf</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns the position of the last occurrence of a character, `c`, in a string `s`. If `s` does not\ncontain `c`, returns `none`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n\nExamples:\n* `\"abcabc\".revPosOf 'a' = some ⟨3⟩`\n* `\"abcabc\".revPosOf 'z' = none`\n* `\"L∃∀N\".revPosOf '∀' = some ⟨4⟩`\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.revPosOf","kind":"def","line":275,"name":"String.Legacy.revPosOf","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L275-L289"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.revPosOfAux\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">revPosOfAux</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">pos</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Auxuliary definition for `String.Legacy.revPosOf`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.revPosOfAux","kind":"def","line":259,"name":"String.Legacy.revPosOfAux","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L259-L273"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.posOf\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">posOf</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns the position of the first occurrence of a character, `c`, in a string `s`. If `s` does not\ncontain `c`, returns `s.rawEndPos`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n\nExamples:\n* `\"abcba\".posOf 'a' = ⟨0⟩`\n* `\"abcba\".posOf 'z' = ⟨5⟩`\n* `\"L∃∀N\".posOf '∀' = ⟨4⟩`\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.posOf","kind":"def","line":243,"name":"String.Legacy.posOf","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L243-L257"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.posOfAux\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">posOfAux</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">stopPos </span><span class=\"fn\">pos</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Auxuliary definition for `String.Legacy.posOf`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.posOfAux","kind":"def","line":227,"name":"String.Legacy.posOfAux","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L227-L241"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.back\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">back</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns the last character in `s`. If `s = \"\"`, returns `(default : Char)`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`. Its runtime behavior is equivalent to that of `String.back`.\n\nExamples:\n* `\"abc\".back = 'c'`\n* `\"\".back = (default : Char)`\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.back","kind":"def","line":213,"name":"String.Legacy.back","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L213-L225"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.front\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">front</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns the first character in `s`. If `s = \"\"`, returns `(default : Char)`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`. Its runtime behavior is equivalent to that of `String.front`.\n\nExamples:\n* `\"abc\".front = 'a'`\n* `\"\".front = (default : Char)`\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.front","kind":"def","line":199,"name":"String.Legacy.front","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L199-L211"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.foldl\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">foldl</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">init</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Folds a function over a string from the left, accumulating a value starting with `init`. The\naccumulated value is combined with each character in order, using `f`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`. Its runtime behavior is equivalent to that of `String.foldl`.\n\nExamples:\n * `\"coffee tea water\".foldl (fun n c => if c.isWhitespace then n + 1 else n) 0 = 2`\n * `\"coffee tea and water\".foldl (fun n c => if c.isWhitespace then n + 1 else n) 0 = 3`\n * `\"coffee tea water\".foldl (·.push ·) \"\" = \"coffee tea water\"`\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.foldl","kind":"def","line":183,"name":"String.Legacy.foldl","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L183-L197"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.foldlAux\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">foldlAux</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">stopPos </span><span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Auxiliary definition for `String.Legacy.foldl`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`. Its runtime behavior is equivalent to that of `String.foldlAux`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.foldlAux","kind":"def","line":168,"name":"String.Legacy.foldlAux","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L168-L181"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.dropWhile\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">dropWhile</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Creates a new string by removing the longest prefix from `s` in which `p` returns `true` for all\ncharacters.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`. Its runtime behavior is equivalent to that of `String.dropWhile`.\n\nExamples:\n* `\"red green blue\".dropWhile (·.isLetter) = \" green blue\"`\n* `\"red green blue\".dropWhile (· == 'r') = \"ed green blue\"`\n* `\"red green blue\".dropWhile (· != 'n') = \"n blue\"`\n* `\"red green blue\".dropWhile (fun _ => true) = \"\"`\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.dropWhile","kind":"def","line":151,"name":"String.Legacy.dropWhile","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L151-L166"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.takeWhile\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">takeWhile</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Creates a new string that contains the longest prefix of `s` in which `p` returns `true` for all\ncharacters.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`. Its runtime behavior is equivalent to that of `String.takeWhile`.\n\nExamples:\n* `\"red green blue\".takeWhile (·.isLetter) = \"red\"`\n* `\"red green blue\".takeWhile (· == 'r') = \"r\"`\n* `\"red green blue\".takeWhile (· != 'n') = \"red gree\"`\n* `\"red green blue\".takeWhile (fun _ => true) = \"red green blue\"`\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.takeWhile","kind":"def","line":134,"name":"String.Legacy.takeWhile","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L134-L149"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.take\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">take</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Creates a new string that contains the first `n` characters (Unicode code points) of `s`.\n\nIf `n` is greater than `s.length`, returns `s`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`. Its runtime behavior is equivalent to that of `String.take`.\n\nExamples:\n* `\"red green blue\".take 3 = \"red\"`\n* `\"red green blue\".take 1 = \"r\"`\n* `\"red green blue\".take 0 = \"\"`\n* `\"red green blue\".take 100 = \"red green blue\"`\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.take","kind":"def","line":116,"name":"String.Legacy.take","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L116-L132"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.drop\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">drop</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Removes the specified number of characters (Unicode code points) from the start of the string.\n\nIf `n` is greater than `s.length`, returns `\"\"`.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`. Its runtime behavior is equivalent to that of `String.drop`.\n\nExamples:\n * `\"red green blue\".drop 4 = \"green blue\"`\n * `\"red green blue\".drop 10 = \"blue\"`\n * `\"red green blue\".drop 50 = \"\"`\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.drop","kind":"def","line":99,"name":"String.Legacy.drop","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L99-L114"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.map\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">map</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Applies the function `f` to every character in a string, returning a string that contains the\nresulting characters.\n\nThis is an old implementation, preserved here for users of the lemmas in\n`Batteries.Data.String.Lemmas`. Its runtime behavior is equivalent to that of `String.map`.\n\nExamples:\n * `\"abc123\".map Char.toUpper = \"ABC123\"`\n * `\"\".map Char.toUpper = \"\"`\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.map","kind":"def","line":84,"name":"String.Legacy.map","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L84-L97"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.mapAux\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Legacy</span>.<span class=\"name\">mapAux</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Implementation of `String.Legacy.map`. ","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.html#String.Legacy.mapAux","kind":"def","line":73,"name":"String.Legacy.mapAux","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/String/Legacy.lean#L73-L82"}}],"imports":["Init"],"instances":[],"name":"Batteries.Data.String.Legacy"}